descriptionNullable:
This dataset is a modified celeb_mini dataset from OpenCV academy. The dataset was used for a facial recognition application, namely the DoppelGander application of the OpenCV Academy course. This is a file of 1179 people with 5 images. Dataset was used for learning of face recognition model of Dlib and OpenFace 

Notebook for scale dataset: https://www.kaggle.com/code/radimkzl/scale-up-celebrity-mini-dataset/edit
